  "text": "Other alternatives to analysis-suitable T-spline are appearing in the literature. These alternatives include hierarchical spline (B-splines, NURBS and T-spline), PHT-splines and LR-splines. In addition to the limited works cited above, the interested reader can be found an overview of the IGA [CITATION_1] .",
